Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來以為只是去一夜情
